Program: Outlook
Title: 29/08/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00x3xyp
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 30 Aug 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the curious case of David Hemler, the man who claims to be an American serviceman who deserted from the air force in 1984. He recently resurfaced in Sweden after living a secret life for 28 years. And the war orphan from Sierra Leone who made her dreams come true by becoming a professional ballerina. Show less